Class JSettingsPanel

java.lang.Object
  java.awt.Component
      java.awt.Container
          javax.swing.JComponent
              javax.swing.JPanel
                  org.sbmlsqueezer.gui.JSettingsPanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class JSettingsPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel

This class is a panel, which contains all necessary options to be specified for an appropriate creation of kinetic laws. It is also a data structure, providing get and set methods to alter the current status of the user settings.
